m/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-8.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e As an official offering from Opera, it comes with usual goodies out of the box. There is a handy reader mode to strip away unnecessary elements from a website, Aria AI (optional GPT-4o or Gemini 1.5), Pinboards to collect, organize, and share links with others, workspaces, and a sidebar to pin your favorite websites.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAnother neat feature is Opera VPN, which prevents third parties from tracking you. Since it’s Chromium-based, Opera Air is compatible with all the extensions from the Chrome Web Store. Everything is neatly implemented and doesn’t overwhelm new users. Overall, Opera has done a decent job with feature additions, and it surely doesn’t feel like a one-month-old browser.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eNow, let’s go over some of the cons you may notice while switching from Chrome or Edge.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"cross-platform-availability\"\u003e\n                        Cross-platform availability\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"with-one-major-exception\"\u003e\n            With one major exception\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2276\" height=\"1312\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Opera Air settings\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-10.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e Opera Air has native apps on Windows and Mac only. Even with Windows, there is no ARM version yet. As for mobile apps, you need to rely on the standard Opera app to sync your browsing history and bookmarks. If you plan to use it on all your devices, you may have inconsistent experiences. If a seamless cross-platform experience is important to you, then you must rely on Chrome or Edge.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"misses-out-on-vertical-tabs\"\u003e\n                        Misses out on vertical tabs\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"a-crucial-part-of-my-workflow\"\u003e\n            A crucial part of my workflow\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2458\" height=\"1468\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Opera Air tabs\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-9.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e Microsoft Edge is my go-to browser for surfing the web. I absolutely love its vertical tabs. I use it all the time on my ultra-wide monitor. So I was bummed to see Opera Air missing out on such a crucial feature. By placing tabs along the side of the screen, they utilize unused horizontal space and offer descriptive tab titles. The absence of this feature in Opera Air feels like a missed opportunity.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"average-tab-management\"\u003e\n                        Average tab management\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"not-the-strongest-part-of-opera-air\"\u003e\n            Not the strongest part of Opera Air\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2426\" height=\"1442\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Opera Air sidebar\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/is-opera-air-as-good-as-chrome-or-edge-11.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e Tab management is simply poor in Opera Air. You can pin important notes or create different workspaces and that’s about it. Unlike Chrome and Edge, there is no way to create tab groups. It’s the one feature I use all the time when researching complex topics. There is no way to collaborate on your workspace tabs either.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"does-opera-air-tick-all-the-boxes-no\"\u003e\n                        Does Opera Air tick all the boxes? No\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOpera’s focus on mindfulness is a unique and commendable concept, and it surely gets the fundamentals of browsing right. However, I’m puzzled as to why Opera decided to launch an entirely new browser rather than integrate these features as an add-on in their existing offering.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eBesides, the lack of Windows ARM support is a significant con if you have one of the latest laptops. For myself, Opera Air doesn\u0026#39;t offer enough compelling reasons to make the leap from Edge. However, I do encourage you to give it a try and see if Opera’s vision for web browsing resonates with your browsing needs. While you are at it, check out these \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/10-browser-extensions-to-power-your-personal-productivity/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ebrowser extensions to power your personal productivity on Opera Air\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                                \n        \n                            \n                                                 